graph TB
    subgraph "ModelMesh Serving Component"
        Controller[modelmesh-controller<br/>Kubernetes Operator]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>Admission Controller]

        Controller -->|validates via| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Runtime Pod Architecture"
        ModelMesh[ModelMesh Container<br/>Java Runtime]
        RESTProxy[REST Proxy<br/>HTTP→gRPC]
        RuntimeAdapter[Runtime Adapter<br/>Sidecar]
        Puller[Storage Helper<br/>Init/Sidecar]
        Runtime[Model Runtime<br/>Triton/MLServer/OpenVINO/TorchServe]

        RESTProxy -->|translates to| ModelMesh
        ModelMesh -->|routes to| RuntimeAdapter
        RuntimeAdapter -->|manages| Runtime
        Puller -->|loads models for| Runtime
    end

    subgraph "External Components"
        ETCD[ETCD<br/>v3.5.9]
        S3[S3 Storage]
        PVC[PVC Storage]
    end

    User[User/Data Scientist] -->|creates| ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime CR]
    User -->|creates| InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService CR]
    User -->|creates| PredictorCR[Predictor CR]

    ServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller
    InferenceServiceCR -->|watched by| Controller
    PredictorCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates/manages| Deployment[Runtime Deployment]
    Controller -->|creates/manages| Service[ClusterIP Service]
    Controller -->|configures| ETCD

    Deployment -->|contains| ModelMesh
    Deployment -->|contains| RESTProxy
    Deployment -->|contains| RuntimeAdapter
    Deployment -->|contains| Runtime
    Deployment -->|init container| Puller

    ModelMesh -->|metadata ops| ETCD
    Puller -->|downloads models| S3
    Puller -->|downloads models| PVC

    Client[External Client] -->|gRPC 8033| Service
    Client -->|HTTP 8008| Service
    Service -->|routes to| ModelMesh

    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes 8443/TCP| Controller
    Prometheus -->|scrapes 2112/TCP| Runtime

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServingRuntimeCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style InferenceServiceCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PredictorCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ETCD fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style S3 fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PVC fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
